Class TemporaryBonus

java.lang.Object
com.example.poo.spaceEntity.Entity
com.example.poo.collectibles.CollectibleEntity
com.example.poo.collectibles.TemporaryBonus
Direct Known Subclasses:
DamageBonus, MovementBonus, SpeedBonus, WeaponBonus
public abstract class TemporaryBonus extends CollectibleEntity
An abstract class representing a temporary bonus collectible entity in the game. It extends the CollectibleEntity class and introduces properties related to time-limited effects.
